data.description: Birdseye perch home with view from upstairs of the mountains over the neighborhood below. 3 bed 3 bath 1,744 square foot two story home close to everything but private on a quiet little side street. Front entry opens into living room with open kitchen and dining room perfect for hosting. Slider leads out to wood deck and flat fully fenced backyard. Upstairs hosts all three bedrooms with master suite windows looking out over city and the mountains stretching across the horizon. Come tour this great home and see it for yourself!
